---
title: Grilled Homestyle Cheese Curd and Turkey Burgers with Zippy Apple Salad
description: This summertime burger is topped with a Quebec classic! It's not quite poutine, but the homemade beef gravy spooned over turkey patties and melted cheese curds is just as delicious! Belly up to the table and get ready to feast!
